    <description>25 mg/m² body surface area (BSA) orally 2 times daily from Days 1 through 21 followed by a 7 day rest period, plus cisplatin 75 mg/m2 BSA on Day 1 each 28 day cycle Number of Cycles: until progression or unacceptable toxicity develops. Treatment with cisplatin is limited to a maximum of 8 cycles.</description>
    <arm_group_label>S-1/cisplatin</arm_group_label>
    <other_name>TS-1, Tegafur/Gimeracil/Oteracil</other_name>
  </intervention>
